componentMetadata.docblock: A component for the continue button to navigate through panels of questions.

childrenComponentProp.name: onButtonClick
childrenComponentProp.docblock: function that changes the path to the next panel or submit.

childrenComponentProp.name: buttonClass
childrenComponentProp.docblock: what CSS class(es) does the button have

childrenComponentProp.name: beforeText
childrenComponentProp.docblock: Stores the value for the icon that will appear before the button text.

childrenComponentProp.name: afterText
childrenComponentProp.docblock: Stores the value for the icon that will appear after the button text.

childrenComponentProp.name: disabled
childrenComponentProp.docblock: is the button disabled or not

childrenComponentProp.name: submitButton
childrenComponentProp.docblock: is this a submit button or not
